## Break-glass
- No model access at the venue? The seeded record IS the demo — all five rows work
  without a single live call. `synth certify --offline` proves suite self-consistency on screen.
- `synth verify` asserts every anchor above before you go on stage; `synth probe`
  validates backdated ingestion on a new host before bulk seeding.

## Reset
Teardown is project-level: fresh project, keys in `.env`, `synth seed` (deterministic —
identical ids). On Cloud free tier use `--config config/cloud-demo.yaml` and check
current event caps first (see that file's header).
